{"tid":1678426,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(正能量) 依家既運動方向是正確的","createTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T16:10:55.000Z","uid":119489,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc6240b0f5f5a6e32a6d0410138da6e0e16da38","tid":1678426,"uid":119489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"今日上BBC中文網，發現有篇文講關於非暴力運動既研究，如果之前有人睇過就 remind 下，未睇過既就可以望下，原文link如下:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert-fut-48720142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Ftrad%2Fvert-fut-48720142&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4buZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=ca290ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Ftrad%2Fvert-fut-48720142&h=985a4bde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert-fut-48720142</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單總結幾點:<br />\n<br />\n1.有3.5%既人出黎非暴力抗爭成功率大增,以香港為例,係616已經有200萬人,佔香港4分1人口,其作用已經非常大。但唔好忘記實際要計埋中國13億人口,實此爭取外國關注,增加支持人數既基數好重要。<br />\n<br />\n2.呢篇文講到和理非既重要性,但我唔係想否定勇武作用,相反勇武先係真正既be water, 能和能勇,只不過裝修等行為要有目的, 勿忘初衷,要多點文宣解釋現在的勇武行為。<br />\n<br />\n在這點上我覺得已經做得很好,外國都不會過量專注裝修而是專注警暴及政治逼害,但當然依然要keep住呢個勢。<br />\n<br />\n3.黃店大大力懲罰,藍店就大大力杯葛。呢個係非常好既方法,係篇文中有提到黑人擺買白人既產品最終白人經濟下降最終要實行平權法例。依家情況亦是如此。"},{"pid":"af01e40df8ca2716146006c9f7939ca0edfb4180","tid":1678426,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"請將今日的警暴情況/記者中槍的tweets推上國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4buZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=d0879510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n入<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> /task1 </span></span>  retweet and like all links<br />\n入<span style=\"color: orange;\">